Package com.dsi.ant.plugins.antplus.pcc

Class AntPlusHeartRatePcc.IpcDefines

java.lang.Object
com.dsi.ant.plugins.antplus.pcc.AntPlusHeartRatePcc.IpcDefines
Enclosing class:
AntPlusHeartRatePcc
public class AntPlusHeartRatePcc.IpcDefines extends Object
Defines the keys and values used to communicate between the PCC and plugin. User code should never have to reference these defines.
